A systematic review and meta-analysis of traditional insect Chinese medicines 
combined chemotherapy for non-surgical hepatocellular carcinoma therapy.

Shi Z(1), Song T(2), Wan Y(3), Xie J(1), Yan Y(1), Shi K(4), Du Y(1), Shang 
L(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Traditional Chinese Medicine, Xijing Hospital Affiliated to 
Fourth Military Medical University, Xi'an, 710032, China.
(2)Department of Orthopaedics, Xi'an City Hospital of Traditional Chinese 
Medicine, Xi'an, 710021, China.
(3)Department of Health Services, the Public Health Faculty of Fourth Military 
